{"tid":826774,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"半賣半送輕小說","createTime":"2018-09-18T12:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T16:20:34.000Z","uid":124116,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"558e8c236334126091820d347a7f3bc74350fc4e","tid":826774,"uid":124116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T12:53:53.000Z","msg":"大家好，小弟我因爲屋企冇乜位，所以想半賣半送咁清左堆書佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/205243_f9c36c8559887f3b9a88eb7e07356cd3.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F205243_f9c36c8559887f3b9a88eb7e07356cd3.JPG&h=158c6647&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/205245_ee122c565569d86da7a4fdb4c0681143.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F205245_ee122c565569d86da7a4fdb4c0681143.JPG&h=fcd00e78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/205246_ef2832fab0973fc783af002f731f733f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F205246_ef2832fab0973fc783af002f731f733f.JPG&h=542d337f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/205248_33196c0dad6aae2f1061140d9a65483f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F205248_33196c0dad6aae2f1061140d9a65483f.JPG&h=47a88987&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/205250_180155a50d1c1488b6a92189ee581d55.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F205250_180155a50d1c1488b6a92189ee581d55.JPG&h=54f46f00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/205251_1b182575a5edaefd889c423316016e5d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F205251_1b182575a5edaefd889c423316016e5d.JPG&h=ba6b8574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/205253_bd15fd1e3822835da613ce3805ef8ebc.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F205253_bd15fd1e3822835da613ce3805ef8ebc.JPG&h=548dc666&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/205254_310ef1054b78f9079ee32b0bc0d51f12.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F205254_310ef1054b78f9079ee32b0bc0d51f12.JPG&h=5f957b43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/205255_2a6460bf7f2a8d56c19151a217ea0996.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F205255_2a6460bf7f2a8d56c19151a217ea0996.JPG&h=fa124300&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/205257_7e5865759008ed18076c79553b2470cf.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F205257_7e5865759008ed18076c79553b2470cf.JPG&h=0935fa48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/205258_beee661f1973e9a47dd08d460ce1dfd2.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F205258_beee661f1973e9a47dd08d460ce1dfd2.JPG&h=e0162d35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁個交收方法係咁：我住係第一城站附近，假如你肯黎拎既話就免費，假如你想我過黎你果度既話，我會要求收返來回地鐵車費（以八達通個價計）。<br />\n請注意我只會係東鐵，馬鐵，藍綠紅線交收。<br />\n<br />\n因為公平起見，現階段每位巴打只可以揀兩套，先到先得，以留言計。有剩低嘅話就會再開post畀大家再拎。<br />\n<br />\n至於有咩書，就係你見到乜就有乜，集數唔清晰嘅話可以再問。另外你會見到一啲散書。假如你已經拎咗一兩套書而想要嘅話，你係可以要埋佢嘅。<br />\n<br />\n啲書我係包左一層包書膠，所以睇上去會有少少令面，至於幾多成新我會話可能有七成掛。因為有膠嘅關係個保養都唔算太差。但係始終係二手書所以唔好預期會全新。另外即使唔鍾意層包書膠，我係唔會幫你拆嘅。<br />\n<br />\n我會留言confirm各巴打，之後請email 各下既聯絡方法（我只有whatsapp冇tg)至 weebhippeastrum@gmail.com，我會係果時再whatsapp同你傾。<br />\n<br />\n多謝各位。"},{"pid":"757833ff88e142a28dc1d377cbc0fae04c403729","tid":826774,"uid":9410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T12:58:35.000Z","msg":"好有心，支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16e3fd29b50439657db09855a8e3c3d47bced87c","tid":826774,"uid":173494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T13:00:04.000Z","msg":"我想要記錄的地平線同sky world<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"012bf3fc5b66f383de61797b08f7ef63398ad8af","tid":826774,"uid":9247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T13:04:35.000Z","msg":"腦選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f290bc13548fa219af787819d163746d7cfcc9","tid":826774,"uid":201282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T13:04:55.000Z","msg":"我想要天鏡的極北之星<br />\nTHX 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90c63977c530c8c8e4d27258e1b32f6e4d0f7e9","tid":826774,"uid":124116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16e3fd29b50439657db09855a8e3c3d47bced87c","tid":826774,"uid":173494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T13:00:04.000Z","msg":"我想要記錄的地平線同sky world<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T13:05:04.000Z","msg":"ok，email你個電話去weebhippeastrum@gmail.com傾交收"},{"pid":"52b02a611189ebc50754dbed201c02140cd1aa18","tid":826774,"uid":124116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"012bf3fc5b66f383de61797b08f7ef63398ad8af","tid":826774,"uid":9247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T13:04:35.000Z","msg":"腦選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T13:06:09.0